      !-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      !  Subroutine   :                     ppm_log
      !-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      !
      !  Purpose      : This routine writes a log message to the ppm log
      !                 file (as defined using ppm_set_unit)
      !
      !  Input        : caller     (C) name of calling subroutine
      !                 mesg       (C) log message
      !
      !  Input/output : 
      !
      !  Output       : info       (I) 0 on success.
      !
      !  Remarks      : 
      !
      !  References   :
      !
      !  Revisions    :
